snippet.title: Predicate Trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/968210/Predicate/

Predicate is a fast paced bullet-hell with a colorful palette and challenging bosses. Move fast and crush enemies as one character, carefully maneuver and shoot enemies as another. The two available characters offer unique ways to play and each have their own upgrade paths. Enjoy the vibrant color palette available or personalize it yourself, customize the visual style to your tastes.

Coming to steam on the 16th of November!

Game made by Ben Martin-Wheatley
Featuring music by Joseph Bailey
